[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cardiff International Pool evacuated as youth taken to hospital

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Cardiff International Pool was evacuated on Tuesday morning and a male youth was taken to hospital.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The pool has now re-opened after the incident at about 11:25 BST.
A Welsh Ambulance Service spokesman said: "We were called to reports of a medical emergency at the Wales International Pool, Cardiff.
"We responded with a rapid response vehicle and a high dependency service vehicle.
"A male youth was taken to University Hospital Wales, Cardiff."
